Dialogue: 0,1:51:13.57,1:51:21.24,BLC-Conan,,0,0,0,,不为谁 只为你
Dialogue: 0,1:51:21.37,1:51:26.54,BLC-Conan,,0,0,0,,因为深爱着你
Dialogue: 0,1:51:34.80,1:51:39.97,BLC-Conan,,0,0,0,,在海边 两人一起看着 sun goes down
Dialogue: 0,1:51:40.10,1:51:45.85,BLC-Conan,,0,0,0,,拿着没喝完的果汁
Dialogue: 0,1:51:47.23,1:51:53.53,BLC-Conan,,0,0,0,,并肩聊着梦想
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.65,1:51:59.41,BLC-Conan,,0,0,0,,想起那一天
